{"tid":1122152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【HeHe 結婚】台北即日受理預約5月24日同性登記結婚","createTime":"2019-04-23T19:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T16:56:40.000Z","uid":24160,"like":19,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e4455f52a8ed259a4f53c66abc296bc0024f3fce","tid":1122152,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T19:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190423/s00004/e147cd97bd5ee926aad634df8122c21e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190423%2Fs00004%2Fe147cd97bd5ee926aad634df8122c21e.jpg&h=f0ed9771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同性婚姻釋憲將滿兩年，台灣行政院早前通過同性婚姻草案，規定年滿18歲的同性伴侶，可成立同性婚姻關係。台北市民政局今日宣布，雖然中央尚未完成相關法律修正或制定，但依照司法院釋字第748號意旨，台北市12間戶政事務所，即日起會受理預約在5月24日舉行的同性結婚登記。<br />\n<br />\n資深同志運動者祁家威早前要求台灣政府，承認他可以跟同性結婚，大法官2017年5月24日承認憲法保障同志婚姻權，並要求主管機關在2年內依其解釋意旨，完成相關法律修正或制定；若逾期未完成法制化，相同性別2人須依民法婚姻章規定，向戶政機關辦理結婚登記。<br />\n<br />\n台北市民政局今日發新聞稿，表示同性伴侶從今年5月24日起，可為經營生活共同的目的，成立具有親密性及排他性的永久結合關係，並指出5月24日為同性婚姻合法化登記首日，台北市各區戶政事務所即日起受理電話及現場預約524同性結婚登記。<br />\n<br />\n行政院會今年2月21日通過「司法院釋字第748號解釋施行法」草案，規定年滿18歲的同性伴侶可成立同性婚姻關係，訂於5月24日施行。在新法案下，同性婚姻有合法財產繼承權及醫療權，可收養血緣子女，並必須遵守單一配偶的相關權利義務。<br />\n<br />\n（綜合報道）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20190423/s00004/1556015334697/%e5%8f%b0%e5%8c%97%e5%8d%b3%e6%97%a5%e5%8f%97%e7%90%86%e9%a0%90%e7%b4%845%e6%9c%8824%e6%97%a5%e5%90%8c%e6%80%a7%e7%99%bb%e8%a8%98%e7%b5%90%e5%a9%9a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20190423%2Fs00004%2F1556015334697%2F%25e5%258f%25b0%25e5%258c%2597%25e5%258d%25b3%25e6%2597%25a5%25e5%258f%2597%25e7%2590%2586%25e9%25a0%2590%25e7%25b4%25845%25e6%259c%258824%25e6%2597%25a5%25e5%2590%258c%25e6%2580%25a7%25e7%2599%25bb%25e8%25a8%2598%25e7%25b5%2590%25e5%25a9%259a&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubP2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=a1948aea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20190423%2Fs00004%2F1556015334697%2F%25e5%258f%25b0%25e5%258c%2597%25e5%258d%25b3%25e6%2597%25a5%25e5%258f%2597%25e7%2590%2586%25e9%25a0%2590%25e7%25b4%25845%25e6%259c%258824%25e6%2597%25a5%25e5%2590%258c%25e6%2580%25a7%25e7%2599%25bb%25e8%25a8%2598%25e7%25b5%2590%25e5%25a9%259a&h=46f0b22e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20190423/s00004/1556015334697/%e5%8f%b0%e5%8c%97%e5%8d%b3%e6%97%a5%e5%8f%97%e7%90%86%e9%a0%90%e7%b4%845%e6%9c%8824%e6%97%a5%e5%90%8c%e6%80%a7%e7%99%bb%e8%a8%98%e7%b5%90%e5%a9%9a</a>"},{"pid":"7f92b1b15be0cc753bacd59fca7324f350319248","tid":1122152,"uid":238370,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T19:59:21.000Z","msg":"當日可以釋到憲都係因為台北市政府入埋稟先做到，所以台北市政府第一個整好同婚注冊登記好應該姐。"},{"pid":"932258e62431b27556db912b40014bba187ba424","tid":1122152,"uid":36775,"like":6,"dislike":29,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T19:59:54.000Z","msg":"Lgbt拎去堆田<br />\n破壞人類文明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e35530da97a2c5889816035d1a2a60d79c625a5","tid":1122152,"uid":238370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T20:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當日可以釋到憲都係因為台北市政府入埋稟先做到，所以台北市政府第一個整好同婚注冊登記好應該姐。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同婚<span style=\"color: red;\">註</span>冊登記"},{"pid":"114d74d3f7f7d891f19157d6c2813666a7c25732","tid":1122152,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T22:13:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2197b03b3544125e32b6c33f0124df5c20cd9c","tid":1122152,"uid":110653,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T23:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor